When I do get money out, I click on the pp and backspace one... so I always remove a random amount of pp... so lets say I have 1829 in the bank, I'd take out 182pp for my shopping. Then when I am done, I convert all the change and put it all back. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em> In Perfect Hate, and Perfect Faith</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
