hehe Once.  I bound myself in CB... ran to the bank... picked up 5000 cp.  Gated.  Announced myself over the zone while Sterling hid nearby.  Instantly I get agro from all the lighties.  The poor sucker that looted me got all that coin.  Couldn't move.  Sterling nailed him.  THEN... he had the balls to scream that we were cheating by hacking the game so he couldn't move.  He couldn't figure it out when he returned to his corpse.  Looted it.  We waited.  He still was screaming at us because he couldn't move.  His guild starting showing up.  Sterling and I both jet being out gunned and out numbered wasn't my idea of fun.  Later we get a tell from one of their officers apologizing for their guildies rude remarks.  He spoke out in guild chat stating that he suddenly had 5000 copper on him and wasn't sure where he got it.<br>
<br>
God that makes me laugh now still. <p>Kithmir, High Elven Wizard<br>
